name: R00T 1g
description:
VIRIDIS SODIUM PANTERUM: A psychogenic stimulant heisted from an incoming supply ship destined for Scrambler City on Aquaburn. Known colloquially as "Green Panther Salt," or more popularly, "R00T"

Derived from ocean salts, crushed and formulated to a lipid, this bottle contains 1 Earth gram. Originally used as a luminol supplement for factory farming and capital punishment, it was discovered to have deep hallucinogenic properties when taken in sizable doses, and has since became a sought after recreational substance across the universe.

Hold 5 or more and burn during the S0lst1ce to create a 1/1 Hallucinogenic Artifact.
